Basic Play
To play a card on the deck it must either be the same suit or the same value.
false
Jacks
When a Jack is played it skips the next person who would have otherwise played.
false
Popcorn
When playing a club you must say popcorn. If popcorn is not said the player recieves a card.
false
Sevens
When a seven is play the turn order is reversed and play proceeds with the in the oppisite direction.
false
Suicide King
When a King of Hearts is played all players must slap the deck. The last player to slap the deck recieves a card.
false